104
00:13:02.147 --> 00:13:04.415
Best friends!

105
00:13:07.586 --> 00:13:09.389
Is this one mine?

106
00:13:09.415 --> 00:13:12.915
Yeah. I already put two in.

107
00:13:14.060 --> 00:13:16.727
