144
00:16:12.539 --> 00:16:15.639
Yeah. well. that was
before all this shit.

145
00:16:29.721 --> 00:16:31.822
What are you doing?

146
00:16:37.096 --> 00:16:40.431
You can keep your promises.
I don't want them.

147
00:16:50.809 --> 00:16:52.743
Haley.

148
